latestIgtvVideos.title: All I needed was 20 mins ? to be free 🙏🏾❤️?
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Ok ! Welcome to my new series! So happy to introduce a journey that we shall take together with @dr.sakina_dhirani_kermali !

She is a highly certified (DDS , MSc , RCSEd , PDC ) professional dentist 🦷 .

I chose to film this because of how professional and polite she was taking me through everything step by step .

So why did I need this :-

Story : Growing up I had an accident , on a staircase and burst my chin open , it was stitched and little did I know my teeth were shaky , months later they slowly discolored , I ignored them and it grew to be my biggest insecurity .

I conquered my fears coz I couldn’t take it anymore , visited her clinic for an all round oral Hygiene , we did a consultation, began with the Teeth cleaning and polishing.

This is part of oral hygiene and involves the removal of dental plaque from teeth. 

As you know , We routinely clean our own teeth by brushing and interdental cleaning, and dentists can remove hardened deposits not removed by routine cleaning.

This was a very easy going process that I didn’t need to get numb before or maybe I’m  just strong and not sensitive 😏🤣 

Personally, I had the best experience and my teeth 🦷 are white as ever , I smile All the freaking time !!

Thank you so much @dr.sakina_dhirani_kermali for giving my smile and confidence back . 

Through the process , we discovered a cavity on one of my molars and because i enjoyed her services I went back after a week it to get fixed. 

I’ll take you through it ! 

You can reach Dr Sakina on +254 715 939933 . 

She does the best Alignment and all her equipments are high end so expect Quality !!! 

Question: After how long do you visit your dentist ? 

Comment down below !

Yes it’s Hygiene * with an E 😩 but it’s posted , we move ❤️

latestIgtvVideos.title: ABAYAS BY SAPPHIRE
IM MIND BLOWN 🤯
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A Very raw review .

Surprise at the end .

This is @saab_bakery_cafe , located at THE WATERFRONT In KAREN .

1. Ambience : Loved the Pinterest vibes ! Everything was well organized , the music was so classic, I felt like I was in Italy/France for a minute ! 
2. Service : TOP NOTCH SERVICE ! everyone was so friendly from when we walked in , sat , the waitress took us through the menu *it being my first time there* , food arrived in time ! They were always around whenever we needed something, asked if we are okay mid eating 🍽 I give them a solid 10 ! 
3. Food presentation: Need I say more ? Just watch the video 😍

Last but not least 
4. TASTE ! : you know those foods you taste and your like OKAY OKAY Flavor 😍🤤 , yes those ones ! Like I miss my plate already ! Thats it ! Saab food has easily become a favorite I can’t wait to try the more . 
I had the *TROPICAL SMOOTHIE* and hands down , satisfaction ! 
Thank you @saab_bakery_cafe ! It was an absolute Pleasure.
